parameters:
Huh?! Lady Konoha... and the king too... does that
mean...

Eek! What's wrong, Lord Konoha! What on earth
happened?!

It's all because of this! Mareus is the one who
created the grimoire called Grimoire.

Ahh... no way... I can't believe you came back...
like that...

Because of you, girls from various worlds have
gone through a lot of trouble.

You may be skilled as a magician, but committing
such crimes is unforgivable. It would be best for
you to receive punishment directly from the king.

I don't understand the concept behind how you can
do such a thing, but it means that you scattered
this Grimoire book across multiple dimensions,
right?

Maybe it's my fault for reading it, but when I
entered the world, I ended up being reincarnated
as the worst person in that world.

For now, I won't treat you poorly in the prison,
so behave yourself a little.

Also, contact Silky Bucks Academy and have them
investigate this Grimoire and seal it properly.

With this... I wonder if we can finally put this
incident to rest...

Hmm, I guess Konoha's breasts are the best at this
size, huh?

The ones that are just starting to swell are the
best, huh~ Ehehehe

You idiot! What are you doing, trying to hide in
the chaos! Seriously, geez!
Ouch... You don't have to hit me that hard...
